<h2 id="nav-containers">
    Containers
    <a href="#nav-containers" class="anchor-link"></a>
</h2>
<p>The containers are optional in Mate, rows and columns can operate without them.</p>
<p>Available containers classes:</p>
<ul class="list-unstyled">
    <li><code>.box</code> - Size of container is fixed to max-width configured id settings.scss ($page__width--maxsize)</li>
    <li><code>.box--fluid</code> - 100% width of container</li>
    <li><code>.box--flex</code> - Container based on flex-box. This class is typicaly used to wrap items (columns), not rows.</li>
</ul>

<div class="code-example code-example--grid">

    <div data-clone>
        <div class="box">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-6">.col-6</div>
                <div class="col-6">.col-6</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

